    {
      "id": "mobile-graph-plan",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Implementation Plan",
      "position": {
        "x": 360,
        "y": 540
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 260,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Suggested Sequence\n\n## Phase 1\n- define mobile intent verbs\n- define touch-first affordances\n- decide where manipulation yields to menus or AI assistance\n\n## Phase 2\n- prototype graph composition without precision layout\n- test traversal, add/connect, and configure loops on phone-sized surfaces\n\n## Phase 3\n- decide which desktop affordances stay desktop-only\n- package mobile as a real mode, not a degraded fallback",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
